 <purpose>
   The Attribute Classification application module supports the requirement
   to provide a value, from a standard set of values, to an attribute on an
   EXPRESS entity. 
   <p>
     The value is represented as a class. 
   </p>
   <note>
     The class may be stored in an external class library.
   </note>
 </purpose>

 <inscope>
   <li>
     the association of a value, represented by a class, to an attribute on
     an entity.
     <note>
       the entities are defined by other modules that extend this module.
     </note>
   </li>
 </inscope>

 <outscope>
